node.text: Your houses have been assigned, now it's time to meet your wizened (and kind of mean, but in a loving way? You know the type we mean) Headmaster, Croak. Where did he come from, and how long has he been here? It's a secret he's held close to his froggy little heart. Because while the founders of the institute remain unnamed, their origins shrouded in secrecy, they entrusted Croak to teach the students about the magic Occultis Aperta ✨within.✨
